'''Ooi Say Hien''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed the [[Critokian]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was picked as the overall winner in the under 16 years old category. He was 13 at the time his entry was published.

